## Instructions
1. `title_disambiguated`: the full title including parenthetical qualifier if present (e.g. "Mercury (planet)"), or null if no disambiguation.
2. `canonical_entity_name`: the clean entity name without disambiguation (e.g. "Mercury").
3. `entity_type`: classify as one of person, place, organization, event, concept, thing, or null.
4. `wikidata_id`: extract the Wikidata QID if available in source fields, otherwise null.

## Output Format
JSON only:
{
  "title_disambiguated": "string|null",
  "canonical_entity_name": "string|null",
  "entity_type": "person|place|organization|event|concept|thing|null",
  "wikidata_id": "string|null"
}
